        "english": "His birthday is approaching, but he doesn't like practical gifts, he prefers personalized ones.",
        "transliteration": "3iid miilado 2areb, bas huwwa ma b7ibb il-hadaya l-3amaliyye, bfaDDel ish-shakhsiyye."
