    {
      "type": "content",
      "content": {
        "title": {
          "english": "Asking for Gift Ideas: 'What should I get him/her?'",
          "arabic": "طلب أفكار للهدايا: 'شو أجيب له/لها؟'"
        },
        "text": "When you're unsure what gift to choose, you can ask for suggestions using 'شو أجيب له/لها؟' (shu ajiib lo/laha?), meaning 'What should I get him/her?'. The 'له' (lo) is for male, and 'لها' (laha) is for female.",
        "examples": [
          {
            "arabic": "شو أجيب له هدية بعيد ميلاده؟",
            "english": "What should I get him for his birthday gift?",
            "transliteration": "Shu ajiib lo hadiyye b-3iid miilado?"
          },
          {
